                 <p/>
               </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="fr">
            <p>Intraduisibile.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="en">
            <p>Not usefully translatable.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="it">
            <p>Intraducibile.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="ar">
            <p>لا يمكن ترجمته بشكل جيد.</p>
         </div><div type="commentary">
                
                <p>This fragment was published by Pugliese Carratelli from a drawing in Oliverio's papers, which is not given. Found in sketchbook VI, it should refer to year 1934.</p>
                <p>It might be fragment a) of <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr016800</ref>, but no checking being possible, we prefer to reedit it as different.</p>
                <p>The date proposed here relies on the fact that <foreign rend="italic">koine</foreign> is used.</p>
                <p/>
            </div></body>
